text: Erest on estewarde on Chelkwilles hevod.
West þanene on catschaga, þanene bi wyrcrumme on langelinch.
Þanene on douelish, þanene bi wyrcrumme on carsford.
Of carsford on witewey, þanene bi wyrcrumme on stikelepaþe.
Þanene on stonberninge, of stonberninge on dunnegete.
Þanene on dunnepool, þanene on dungraf, þanene on red þorn.
Þanene on slap, þanene on eþynford, þanene on rith on rugelege.
Þanene on caducburne on strim, þanne on manneswyþyg.
Þanene on dikedene ford on strim at eswelleschyt on yle.
Þanene on riht on landbrok on strim.
